        "Data": [
          "<h1>Applies to</h1>\n  <ul>\n    <li>C&#43;&#43;</li>\n  </ul>\n  <h1>What to Do</h1>\n  <p>Bind sockets to specific IP addresses.</p>\n  <h1>Why</h1>\n  <p>Binding sockets to specific IP addresses, instead of INADDR_ANY, prevents socket hijacking.</p>\n  <h1>When</h1>\n  <p>Use this guideline when writing server applications using IP sockets.</p>\n  <h1>How</h1>\n  <p>Bind sockets to specific IP addresses, instead of to INADDR_ANY. For Windows, set the SO_EXCLUSIVEADDRUSE option, which protects against binding to the same port.</p>"
